```plantuml
@startuml IBM_customer-sentiment-on-seller-quality-nlu-cp4d
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "Jupyter Notebook" as Notebook #lightsteelblue

rectangle "Watson NLU" as WatsonNLU #lightyellow

rectangle "Db2 Database" as Db2 #aliceblue

rectangle "Embedded Dashboard\nService" as Dashboard #lightgreen

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> Notebook : Execute data processing pipeline

' Jupyter Notebook interactions
Notebook --> Db2 : Load refined customer review data
Notebook --> WatsonNLU : Perform sentiment and emotion analysis
WatsonNLU --> Notebook : Return sentiment scores

Notebook -> Notebook : Calculate seller quality ratings
Notebook --> Dashboard : Generate dataset for visualization

User --> Dashboard : Explore seller and product performance

@enduml
```